product_description.downstream_description:
Constructed from a breathable material, the Swede-O Elastic Wrist Brace comfortably supports the wrist in a cock-up position. The contoured aluminum stay significantly reduces wrist motions, allowing the wrist to rest by minimizing motions that may aggravate nerves, tendons, or ligaments. Ideal for carpal tunnel syndrome, RSI, acute or chronic wrist pain. The adjustable thumb and wrist closures for easy application and a custom fit. The elastic webbing material stretches and contours to the natural shape of the wrist and hand for increased comfort and support. It is a breathable, durable elastic material. This support is ideal for carpal tunnel syndrome, RSI (Repetitive Stress Injuries), acute or chronic wrist pain or irritation, postoperative pain, post-traumatic pain, tendonitis, arthritis and osteoarthritis. Specify left or right hand when ordering, allows full use of fingers. Made in the USA and contains no latex.

How to meaasure: evently around the wrist joint.
  • S: 5 1/2"-6 1/2" 14-17cm
  • M: 6 3.4"-7 1/2" 17-19cm/li>
  • L: 7 3/4"-8 1/2" 20-22cm/li>
  • XL: 8 3/4-9 1/2" 22-24cm/li>
